{"tid":2216313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（口臭廢老）3月霸氣表示「我會去搵武肺」","createTime":"2020-09-24T14:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T05:47:06.000Z","uid":1426,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7c1f0b19c65ba83dfa93f15113f98b288d97a9","tid":2216313,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"意甲球隊AC米蘭繼周三先有後衞里奧杜亞迪確診武漢肺炎後，周四米蘭在官方網站宣佈，就連38歲的球星伊巴謙莫域同樣在病毒測試中呈陽性，球員需要立即進行隔離，意味着稍後時間上演的歐霸盃第3圈外圍賽，主場對陣波杜基林特一戰，伊巴將無緣上陣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3jpkVP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3jpkVP.png&h=2682ce06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實早在今年3月意大利正值武漢肺炎疫情高峯期時，當時伊巴就曾在IG上發佈一條短片，更在片中提到：「如果病毒沒有來找Zlatan（伊巴名字），Zlatan就會去找他。」事隔6個月，伊巴不幸地感染武肺，未知這位瑞典球星會否後悔自己曾經說過這番話。"},{"pid":"5953d91b46215af92c20cecae2caf4621fb5bb54","tid":2216313,"uid":41524,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去死啦柒頭"},{"pid":"0d066c27d38b2b0e950e4ae8a284791bf693e3cb","tid":2216313,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff2c953eefa750bced078262db7ff5c01a73382","tid":2216313,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d066c27d38b2b0e950e4ae8a284791bf693e3cb","tid":2216313,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"麻友？"},{"pid":"02ca7bd9a46bf5415cbc033c2c73a234c40202b4","tid":2216313,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ff2c953eefa750bced078262db7ff5c01a73382","tid":2216313,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d066c27d38b2b0e950e4ae8a284791bf693e3cb","tid":2216313,"ui